title: Now That's Music - August(Deluxe 2-CD) 2016 320ak
description:
Now That's Music - August(Deluxe 2-CD) 2016 320ak

Once again here we are back with a mixture of fresh new Hard Rock and Metal.
But I got overly inspired and threw in some of my older favorites in as well but Im not worried cause Im sure that you guys will like em to. 

A lot has happened since the last installment of this series. I predicted the fall of Kat. And even though it still was a shocker. But it happens it's not the first index to fall and it wont be the last. And it looks like the odds on favorite to fill the void Is Extra Torrent.
Well good luck, the top spot is a coveted and yet deadly spot to have. Enough of my
talking thats not why were here lets get to the...

Until the next time
